## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
|---|---|
| Cloud | AWS EC2, S3, DynamoDB, SNS, ECR |
| CI/CD | Jenkins, Jenkinsfile |
| Containerisation | Docker, Docker Compose |
| Backend | Python 3.9 |
| Testing | Python unittest |
| Version Control | Git, GitHub |
| OS | Ubuntu 24.04 LTS |

---

## 🚨 Fraud Detection Rules

| Rule | Condition | Flag Reason |
|---|---|---|
| High Amount | Transaction > £10,000 | HIGH_AMOUNT |
| Suspicious Location | Country in [XX, ZZ, KP, IR] | SUSPICIOUS_LOCATION |
| Odd Hours | Transaction between 1am - 4am | ODD_HOURS |
| Missing Fields | Required fields missing | MISSING_FIELDS |

